1
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:09,360
Young Master.

2
00:01:09,880 --> 00:01:10,400
It's so late.

3
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:11,280
Why are you here?

4
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:13,200
Uncle Yan,

5
00:01:14,360 --> 00:01:15,520
take a look at the man in this photo.

6
00:01:16,440 --> 00:01:17,360
Is it Liu Jiaquan?

7
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:23,480
That's right.

8
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:24,400
It's him.

9
00:01:25,040 --> 00:01:26,040
Although the photo is a bit blurry,

10
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:27,520
I can confirm

11
00:01:29,040 --> 00:01:30,040
that this is Liu Jiaquan.

12
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:34,200
So it really is him.

13
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:41,040
I found this photo at home.

14
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:42,760
I've already confirmed it with Uncle Yan.

15
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:46,400
The one standing next to my father

16
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:48,040
is Liu Jiaquan.

17
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:54,480
I brought you guys some good food.

18
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,320
What are you looking at?

19
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:04,600
The man in this photo...

20
00:02:08,200 --> 00:02:08,760
You know him?

21
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,120
Master?

22
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,200
He's your Master?

23
00:02:19,760 --> 00:02:21,200
I just think

24
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:22,480
the man in the photo

25
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:25,000
looks a lot like my Master.

26
00:02:25,640 --> 00:02:26,720
I'm not entirely sure either.

27
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:50,720
Inspector,

28
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:52,280
these past few days,

29
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,360
we visited the places Yihe

30
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:54,360
used to frequent.

31
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:55,840
The people he interacted with

32
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,200
either kept their mouths shut

33
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:59,040
or claimed to know nothing.

34
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:00,560
In my opinion,

35
00:03:01,040 --> 00:03:01,840
someone must have

36
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:02,840
silenced them.

37
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:05,040
The more they act like this,

38
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:06,400
the more it proves

39
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,120
he has some hidden secrets.

40
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:09,120
Yeah.

41
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:10,480
By the way,

42
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:11,880
right now in the city,

43
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:13,520
General Ling's guards are everywhere.

44
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:15,320
They're acting suspiciously,

45
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:16,600
and I don't know what they're up to.

46
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:20,560
The people around my father,

47
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:22,080
these so-called brothers-in-arms,

48
00:03:22,720 --> 00:03:24,000
none of them are easy to deal with.

49
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:26,840
We need to have our men

50
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,440
work a bit harder

51
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:30,440
to keep a close eye on their every move.

52
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:32,320
Understood.

53
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,000
You're back!

54
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:49,560
Where have you been these past few days?

55
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:50,880
You didn't even take me with you.

56
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:52,160
Well,

57
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:53,720
recently,

58
00:03:54,720 --> 00:03:56,240
my uncles have caused me

59
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:56,800
a bunch of trouble, that's all.

60
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:57,720
It's nothing.

61
00:03:59,440 --> 00:03:59,960
Qingqing,

62
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:01,320
when I was sick,

63
00:04:01,320 --> 00:04:02,280
you were always taking care of me.

64
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:03,960
I wanted you to get some good rest,

65
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,000
so I didn't call you.

66
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:08,120
What's wrong?

67
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:09,400
Did you need me for something?

68
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:11,600
No.

69
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:13,280
It's just that

70
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:15,120
I haven't seen you for days.

71
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,120
Today I have to sort out

72
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:18,800
my father's belongings.

73
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:19,880
I'll head upstairs first.

74
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:04,320
It's so late.

75
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:06,440
Why haven't you rested yet?

76
00:05:08,280 --> 00:05:09,280
I brought you a late-night snack.

77
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:11,520
Are you...

78
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:14,080
hiding something from me?

79
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,280
You're overthinking it.

80
00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:17,440
I'm just

81
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:18,280
sorting out my father's

82
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:18,960
belongings, that's all.

83
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:20,080
Seeing

84
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:22,200
if I can find any clues in them.

85
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:24,640
Are you investigating

86
00:05:24,640 --> 00:05:25,640
my Master, Yihe?

87
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:30,560
You kept it from me

88
00:05:31,280 --> 00:05:32,400
because you were afraid I'd leak

89
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:33,760
information to my Master, right?

90
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:36,640
Huang Jinrong,

91
00:05:37,760 --> 00:05:39,200
you just don't trust me.

92
00:05:41,640 --> 00:05:42,560
I don't distrust you.

93
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:44,880
It's just that he is your Master, after all.

94
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:46,640
I didn't want to drag you into this.

95
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:50,000
Don't you know?

96
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:53,080
Doing this puts me in a tougher spot.

97
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:33,880
The person in this photo is...

98
00:06:34,840 --> 00:06:35,760
You know him?

99
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:38,200
Master.

100
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:40,440
He is your Master?

101
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:49,880
Master...

102
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:51,840
Could it be...

103
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:54,280
Are you really involved in

104
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:54,960
the Huang family murders?

105
00:07:05,400 --> 00:07:05,760
Qingqing.

106
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:07,520
Why isn't the Inspector here for breakfast yet?

107
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,200
Inspector.

108
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:24,640
Come and sit.

109
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:49,840
Qingqing.

110
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:54,880
I'm done eating.

111
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:02,760
Inspector,

112
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,640
did you make Qingqing mad?

113
00:08:08,520 --> 00:08:09,280
She knows we are

114
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:10,120
investigating her Master.

115
00:08:10,960 --> 00:08:11,880
She says I don't trust her.

116
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:16,320
Tell me, why is a girl's mind

117
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:17,960
so hard to figure out?

118
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:24,200
I really didn't expect

119
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:25,880
words about figuring out girls

120
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:27,880
to actually come out of your mouth.

121
00:08:30,880 --> 00:08:31,400
Inspector,

122
00:08:32,880 --> 00:08:33,400
why don't you

123
00:08:33,560 --> 00:08:34,880
just tell Qingqing the truth

124
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:36,560
about everything in detail?

125
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:37,560
Perhaps

126
00:08:37,880 --> 00:08:39,280
she would understand your good intentions.

127
00:08:41,520 --> 00:08:42,520
She's furious right now.

128
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:43,960
Why would she listen to my explanation?

129
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:48,760
Besides, I'm afraid if she knows the truth,

130
00:08:50,280 --> 00:08:50,960
she'll be in danger.

131
00:09:00,760 --> 00:09:01,400
Why are you here?

132
00:09:02,520 --> 00:09:03,760
Who could stop me?

133
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:09,280
I wonder why the Sorceress

134
00:09:09,880 --> 00:09:10,640
has come this time.

135
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:14,720
Huang Jinrong.

136
00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:16,440
Look at the state of you.

137
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:18,200
Still vainly trying to find the truth?

138
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:21,000
It's utterly ridiculous.

139
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:22,200
What do you mean?

140
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:25,280
You think you can find out

141
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:26,520
absolutely everything?

142
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:29,400
In fact, your every move

143
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:31,760
is completely under his control.

144
00:09:33,880 --> 00:09:34,880
This "he" you speak of,

145
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:37,840
who is it?

146
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:43,960
Huang Jinrong,

147
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:45,840
you need to be careful.

148
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:47,560
Your face is ashen,

149
00:09:47,560 --> 00:09:48,440
darkness between the brows.

150
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:49,800
One look,

151
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:52,080
and it's clear your vital energy is fading,

152
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,800
a sign your time is near.

153
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:59,640
I am talking to a dead man.
